    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Top, tail, peel and grate you <strong>carrot[s]</strong></p><p>Wash your<strong> salad </strong>then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Combine the <strong>grated carrot</strong> and<strong> salad </strong>in a large bowl – this is your<strong> salad mix</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1665486475319-x200.jpg",
