            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Drain your <strong>sweetcorn</strong></p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>drained sweetcorn</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and cook for 4-5 min or until starting to char</p><p>Once starting to char, transfer to a bowl to cool slightly, reserving the pan – this is your <strong>charred sweetcorn</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1665486486809-x200.jpg",
