            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pan to a medium-high heat with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, drain then add your <strong>king prawns</strong> and <strong>chopped garlic </strong>and cook for 4-5 min or until the prawns are cooked through – these are your <strong>garlic king prawns</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1665486490913-x200.jpg",
