          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-copy-1665486513436-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>potato & sweetcorn salad</strong> in bowls and top with the <strong>garlic king prawns</strong> and <strong>quick-pickled red onion</strong></p><p>Drizzle over the <strong>zingy chipotle mayo</strong> and garnish with a <strong>lime wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
